@startuml
title Diagrama de Estados - Game (Estado Atual)

[*] --> Starting

Starting : status = Starting
Starting : State = GameStartingState
Starting --> Playing : GameStartingState.Update()

Playing : status = IN_PROGRESS
Playing : State = GamePlayingState
Playing --> Playing : PlayCard() + UpdateRoundState()
Playing --> Playing : Round terminou e score < 4\n(nova Round)
Playing --> Finished : score de equipa >= 4

Finished : status = FINISHED
Finished : State = GameFinishedState
Finished : emite GAME_ENDED
Finished --> [*]

@enduml
